{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1209950/extras/RaceCondition.gif?t=1673514123\" /><br>So, you've got a place in the world tour... Congratulations! But, you're a newcomer, and now you will need to prove yourself. This game lets you fight your way up the ranks as you compete in races across the globe. If you're too good, however, you will certainly trigger resistance from the more experienced drivers. Do you think you are up for the challenge?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FAST &amp; STYLIZED RACING</h2>Easy to pick up and learn. A bit harder to master. Race Condition offers an exciting challenge with fast gameplay and intelligent AI opponents.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">MULTIPLE GAME MODES</h2>Play the <strong>World Tour</strong> to increase your Driver Level and unlock new tracks. Or score a new lap record in <strong>Time Trial</strong>. <br>Having friends over? Challenge them to some exhilarating <strong>Split Screen</strong> racing.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A VARIETY OF TRACKS</h2>The game offers <strong>21 tracks</strong> in 11 destinations across the world. You will encounter various race conditions, such as sun, rain, fog, snow, day and night driving.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1209950/extras/ThreeAttractLoops.gif?t=1673514123\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">MORE DETAILS</h2><strong>Online Leaderboards</strong><br>Compare your results with other drivers in the online leaderboards. Drive well and you might even beat the global track records!<br><br><strong>Intelligent AI-Driven Opponents</strong><br>The other cars present a fun challenge by reacting intelligently to the situations that can occur during a race. Can you outsmart them and win?<br><br><strong>Split-screen Multiplayer</strong><br>Play with friends in split screen mode. The game supports 2-4 simultaneous players.<br><br><strong>Finely Tuned Game Physics</strong><br>Entirely physics driven, the game offers a rewarding driving experience. Unlike many other racing games, the AI cars are also driven by the same physics model, so it's all fair play.<br><br><strong>Great Soundtrack</strong><br>Turn up the volume and enjoy the retro inspired soundtrack as you cruise along the various tracks.<br><br><strong>Keyboard And Controller Support</strong><br>Play with keyboard or controller, or any combination of those (in split screen mode).<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1209950/extras/rclogo.png?t=1673514123\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"5 Gold","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1209950/52b8dafc62ab399a135840fbf1e2aa3702afa9ff.jpg"},{"name":"Gold","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1209950/2e37074a6e586ab502f39cf0c95c0a9388183a63.jpg"},{"name":"10 Gold","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1209950/1149f695407b966ea16f460882fbe54bd700dfba.jpg"},{"name":"Completionist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1209950/d7d5a6dc65637393604e379e59f819d9f4672404.jpg"},{"name":"400","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1209950/f7bef5591b52a1f7052487bce75c7bf85b1351d6.jpg"},{"name":"450","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1209950/14f0abdc101a687113c25844377f0ef501cf0f95.jpg"},{"name":"Best Lap","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1209950/f36e34c1fe2f41a649088c68f8d2ae5b084f3771.jpg"},{"name":"Fastest Car","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1209950/56ae93cf564f038a405ac7bfd5fc245592fc6435.jpg"},{"name":"Whiplash","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1209950/f58af21e4fe99b13c597f2da2113d9b644d0